1441ir_node *new_rd_Load(dbg_info *dbgi, ir_node *block, ir_node * irn_mem, ir_node * irn_ptr, ir_mode* mode, ir_type* type, ir_cons_flags flags)
1442{
1443
1444 ir_graph *irg = get_irn_irg(block);
1445
1446 ir_node *in[2];
1447 in[0] = irn_mem;
1448 in[1] = irn_ptr;
1449
1450 ir_node *res = new_ir_node(dbgi, irg, block, op_Load, mode_T, 2, in);
1451 load_attr *attr = &res->attr.load;
1452 attr->mode = mode;
1453 attr->type = type;
1454 attr->volatility = flags & cons_volatile ? volatility_is_volatile : volatility_non_volatile;
1455 attr->unaligned = flags & cons_unaligned ? align_non_aligned : align_is_aligned;
1456 attr->exc.pinned = flags & cons_floats ? op_pin_state_floats : op_pin_state_pinned;
1457 attr->exc.throws_exception = (flags & cons_throws_exception) != 0;
1458 verify_new_node(res);
1459 res = optimize_node(res);
1460 return res;
1461}

2618ir_node *new_rd_Store(dbg_info *dbgi, ir_node *block, ir_node * irn_mem, ir_node * irn_ptr, ir_node * irn_value, ir_type* type, ir_cons_flags flags)
2619{
2620
2621 ir_graph *irg = get_irn_irg(block);
2622
2623 ir_node *in[3];
2624 in[0] = irn_mem;
2625 in[1] = irn_ptr;
2626 in[2] = irn_value;
2627
2628 ir_node *res = new_ir_node(dbgi, irg, block, op_Store, mode_T, 3, in);
2629 store_attr *attr = &res->attr.store;
2630 attr->type = type;
2631 attr->volatility = flags & cons_volatile ? volatility_is_volatile : volatility_non_volatile;
2632 attr->unaligned = flags & cons_unaligned ? align_non_aligned : align_is_aligned;
2633 attr->exc.pinned = flags & cons_floats ? op_pin_state_floats : op_pin_state_pinned;
2634 attr->exc.throws_exception = (flags & cons_throws_exception) != 0;
2635 verify_new_node(res);
2636 res = optimize_node(res);
2637 return res;
2638}
